OL,3,CCumbria Police see increase in hate
OL,4,Ccrime and knife crime in annual figures
OL,6,FThe performance of Cumbria Police has
OL,7,Fcome under scrutiny this week as the
OL,8,Fforce went through their annual Public
OL,9,FAccountability Conference.
OL,11,FSenior policing figures met with the
OL,12,FPolice, Fire and Crime Commissioner
OL,13,F(PFCC) to discuss the performance of
OL,14,Fthe constabulary in the last year.
OL,16,FThey reviewed a report looking into
OL,17,Fthe number of crimes reported and how
OL,18,Fthe force dealt with them.
OL,20,FWhat are some of the key figures?
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
