OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1781884084
OL,3,CCumbria Police see increase in hate
OL,4,Ccrime and knife crime in annual figures
OL,6,FIt found that hate crime increased by
OL,7,F19.9% in the last financial year.
OL,9,FThat was primarily driven by racially
OL,10,Faggravated offences - which are up by
OL,11,F33.8% - and offences against
OL,12,Ftransgender people which are up 50% on
OL,13,Flast year.
OL,15,FKnife crime has also seen a 14.1%
OL,16,Fincrease with 22 more crimes
OL,17,Fidentified as knife crime in 2025/26.
OL,19,FCumbria's PFCC, David Allen said:
OL,20,F"Hate crime is a concern, you know,
OL,21,Fthere's a national picture here.
OL,26,@|D@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
