CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1781884084
OL,3,CCumbria Police see increase in hate
OL,4,Ccrime and knife crime in annual figures
OL,6,F"But locally, the constabulary, my
OL,7,Foffice, and other agencies are putting
OL,8,Fa lot of effort into early schooling.
OL,10,F"(Such as) centre policing, education
OL,11,Fat the schools, and citizenship
OL,12,Fawareness to make sure people
OL,13,Funderstand that you have rights, but
OL,14,Fyou have responsibilities that go with
OL,15,Fthose rights."
OL,17,FHe went on to explain that: "if a hate
OL,18,Fcrime is reported, the constabulary
OL,19,Fwill deal with it properly and
OL,20,Fappropriately."
