OL,3,CCumbria Police see increase in hate
OL,4,Ccrime and knife crime in annual figures
OL,6,FDespite challenges highlighted in the
OL,7,Freport, the force remains proud of its
OL,8,Fpublic engagement metrics. Cumbria
OL,9,FPolice currently holds the highest
OL,10,Ffigure nationally in a survey asking
OL,11,Fresidents if they believe "the police
OL,12,Fwould treat them with respect,"
OL,13,Fscoring 88.2% compared to the national
OL,14,Faverage of 82.6%.
